{"type":"message","id":"8fd5dd2e","parentId":"82e79434","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:07.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the structure, the MCP tools are implemented in the src/tools/mcp/doc/ directory. The update.js file should contain the update-doc implementation. However, I need to understand how these tools are exposed and callable.\n\nSince I'm an OpenClaw agent, these tools should be registered and available through the OpenClaw runtime. The tools are MCP (Model Context Protocol) based and should be callable via the runtime's tool calling mechanism.\n\nLet me check the update.js to understand the tool signature better, and then figure out how to call it.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ef6ba553d32240a7a0749d26","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/src/tools/mcp/doc/update.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":160,"cacheRead":16605,"cacheWrite":437,"totalTokens":17208,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000044800000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00004546}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774003744643}}
{"type":"message","id":"9dda165d","parentId":"8fd5dd2e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:07.579Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ef6ba553d32240a7a0749d26","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"use strict\";\n/**\n * Copyright (c) 2026 ByteDance Ltd. and/or its affiliates\n * SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT\n *\n * MCP update-doc 工具\n * 更新云文档（overwrite/append/replace_range/replace_all/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range，支持异步 task_id 查询）\n */\nimport { Type } from '@sinclair/typebox';\nimport { registerMcpTool } from '../shared';\n// Schema 定义\nconst UpdateDocSchema = Type.Object({\n    doc_id: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: '文档 ID 或 URL' })),\n    markdown: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: 'Markdown 内容' })),\n    mode: Type.Union([\n        Type.Literal('overwrite'),\n        Type.Literal('append'),\n        Type.Literal('replace_range'),\n        Type.Literal('replace_all'),\n        Type.Literal('insert_before'),\n        Type.Literal('insert_after'),\n        Type.Literal('delete_range'),\n    ], { description: '更新模式（必填）' }),\n    selection_with_ellipsis: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: '定位表达式：开头内容...结尾内容（与 selection_by_title 二选一）' })),\n    selection_by_title: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: '标题定位：例如 ## 章节标题（与 selection_with_ellipsis 二选一）' })),\n    new_title: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: '新的文档标题（可选）' })),\n    task_id: Type.Optional(Type.String({ description: '异步任务 ID，用于查询任务状态' })),\n});\n// 参数验证\nfunction validateUpdateDocParams(p) {\n    if (p.task_id)\n        return;\n    if (!p.doc_id) {\n        throw new Error('update-doc：未提供 task_id 时必须提供 doc_id');\n    }\n    const needSelection = p.mode === 'replace_range' || p.mode === 'insert_before' || p.mode === 'insert_after' || p.mode === 'delete_range';\n    if (needSelection) {\n        const hasEllipsis = Boolean(p.selection_with_ellipsis);\n        const hasTitle = Boolean(p.selection_by_title);\n        if ((hasEllipsis && hasTitle) || (!hasEllipsis && !hasTitle)) {\n            throw new Error('update-doc：mode 为 replace_range/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range 时，selection_with_ellipsis 与 selection_by_title 必须二选一');\n        }\n    }\n    const needMarkdown = p.mode !== 'delete_range';\n    if (needMarkdown && !p.markdown) {\n        throw new Error(`update-doc：mode=${p.mode} 时必须提供 markdown`);\n    }\n}\n/**\n * 注册 update-doc 工具\n */\nexport function registerUpdateDocTool(api) {\n    registerMcpTool(api, {\n        name: 'feishu_update_doc',\n        mcpToolName: 'update-doc',\n        toolActionKey: 'feishu_update_doc.default',\n        label: 'Feishu MCP: update-doc',\n        description: '更新云文档（overwrite/append/replace_range/replace_all/insert_before/insert_after/delete_range，支持异步 task_id 查询）',\n        schema: UpdateDocSchema,\n        validate: validateUpdateDocParams,\n    });\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774003747573}}
{"type":"message","id":"18c41cd7","parentId":"9dda165d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:10.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand the tool structure. The tool is registered as `feishu_update_doc` and it's an MCP tool that should be callable through the OpenClaw runtime. \n\nSince I'm running inside OpenClaw as a subagent, I should be able to call this tool. However, the tool isn't available as a direct CLI command. Let me check if there's a way to call MCP tools directly or if I need to use a different approach.\n\nLet me look at the shared.js to understand how MCP tools are called:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_495d2c260cfb45898a456e87","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/src/tools/mcp/shared.js","limit":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":170,"cacheRead":17042,"cacheWrite":910,"totalTokens":18128,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000047600000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00004826}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774003747580}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1ec8432","parentId":"18c41cd7","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:10.630Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_495d2c260cfb45898a456e87","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"use strict\";\n/**\n * Copyright (c) 2026 ByteDance Ltd. and/or its affiliates\n * SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT\n *\n * MCP 工具的共享代码（所有业务域共享）\n * 包含：MCP 客户端、类型定义、通用辅助函数\n */\nimport { createToolContext, formatToolResult, registerTool } from '../helpers';\nimport { handleInvokeErrorWithAutoAuth } from '../oapi/helpers';\nimport { getUserAgent } from '../../core/version';\nimport { mcpDomain } from '../../core/domains';\nimport fs from 'node:fs';\nimport path from 'node:path';\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// 辅助函数\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\nexport function isRecord(v) {\n    return typeof v === 'object' && v !== null;\n}\n/**\n * 从配置对象中提取 MCP endpoint URL\n */\nexport function extractMcpUrlFromConfig(cfg) {\n    if (!isRecord(cfg))\n        return undefined;\n    const channels = cfg.channels;\n    if (!isRecord(channels))\n        return undefined;\n    const feishu = channels.feishu;\n    if (!isRecord(feishu))\n        return undefined;\n    const url = feishu.mcpEndpoint;\n    const legacyUrl = feishu.mcp_url;\n    const chosen = typeof url === 'string' ? url : typeof legacyUrl === 'string' ? legacyUrl : undefined;\n    if (typeof chosen !== 'string')\n        return undefined;\n    const trimmed = chosen.trim();\n    return trimmed ? trimmed : undefined;\n}\n/**\n * 部分 MCP 网关/代理会在 result 内再次包一层 JSON-RPC envelope。\n * 这里做一次递归解包，确保工具最终返回的是纯 result JSON（不包含 jsonrpc/id）。\n */\nexport function unwrapJsonRpcResult(v) {\n    if (!isRecord(v))\n        return v;\n    const hasJsonRpc = typeof v.jsonrpc === 'string';\n    const hasId = 'id' in v;\n    const hasResult = 'result' in v;\n    const hasError = 'error' in v;\n    if (hasJsonRpc && (hasResult || hasError)) {\n        if (hasError) {\n            const err = v.error;\n            if (isRecord(err) && typeof err.message === 'string') {\n                throw new Error(err.message);\n            }\n            throw new Error('MCP 返回 error，但无法解析 message');\n        }\n        return unwrapJsonRpcResult(v.result);\n    }\n    // 某些实现可能只包了 { result: ... } 而没有 jsonrpc 字段\n    if (!hasJsonRpc && !hasId && hasResult && !hasError) {\n        return unwrapJsonRpcResult(v.result);\n    }\n    return v;\n}\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// MCP 配置管理\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\nlet mcpEndpointOverride;\nexport function setMcpEndpointOverride(endpoint) {\n    mcpEndpointOverride = endpoint;\n}\nfunction readMcpUrlFromOpenclawJson() {\n    // 优先读取工作目录下的 `.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n    // 约定：channels.feishu.mcpEndpoint（兼容旧字段 mcp_url）\n    try {\n        const p = path.join(process.cwd(), '.openclaw', 'openclaw.json');\n        if (!fs.existsSync(p))\n            return undefined;\n        const raw = fs.readFileSync(p, 'utf8');\n        const cfg = JSON.parse(raw);\n        return extractMcpUrlFromConfig(cfg);\n    }\n    catch {\n        // 配置缺失/JSON 解析失败等情况，忽略并回退到默认逻辑\n        return undefined;\n    }\n}\nfunction getMcpEndpoint(brand) {\n    // 优先级：运行时覆盖 > 配置文件 > 环境变量 > 基于 brand 的默认值\n    return (mcpEndpointOverride ||\n        readMcpUrlFromOpenclawJson() ||\n        process.env.FEISHU_MCP_ENDPOINT?.trim() ||\n        `${mcpDomain(brand)}/mcp`);\n}\nfunction buildAuthHeader() {\n    // 允许通过环境变量注入鉴权（若服务端要求）\n    const token = process.env.FEISHU_MCP_BEARER_TOKEN?.trim() || process.env.FEISHU_MCP_TOKEN?.trim();\n\n[128 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774003750621}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fbf5a21","parentId":"c1ec8432","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:12.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I see that MCP tools are called via HTTP requests to an MCP endpoint. Let me continue reading to understand how the actual tool calls are made:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0a506b1fc72a4aeb82bff57f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/src/tools/mcp/shared.js","offset":101,"limit":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":102,"cacheRead":17952,"cacheWrite":1173,"totalTokens":19233,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00002856,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00002922}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774003750631}}
{"type":"message","id":"820dedd3","parentId":"7fbf5a21","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:12.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_0a506b1fc72a4aeb82bff57f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if (!token)\n        return undefined;\n    return token.toLowerCase().startsWith('bearer ') ? token : `Bearer ${token}`;\n}\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// MCP JSON-RPC 客户端\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n/**\n * 调用 MCP 工具\n * @param name MCP 工具名称\n * @param args 工具参数\n * @param toolCallId 工具调用 ID\n * @param uat 用户访问令牌(由 invoke 权限检查后传入)\n * @param brand 当前账号品牌，用于选择 MCP 端点域名\n */\nexport async function callMcpTool(name, args, toolCallId, uat, brand) {\n    const endpoint = getMcpEndpoint(brand);\n    const auth = buildAuthHeader();\n    const body = {\n        jsonrpc: '2.0',\n        id: toolCallId,\n        method: 'tools/call',\n        params: {\n            name,\n            arguments: args,\n        },\n    };\n    const headers = {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'X-Lark-MCP-UAT': uat,\n        'X-Lark-MCP-Allowed-Tools': name,\n        'User-Agent': getUserAgent(),\n    };\n    if (auth)\n        headers.authorization = auth;\n    const res = await fetch(endpoint, {\n        method: 'POST',\n        headers,\n        body: JSON.stringify(body),\n    });\n    const text = await res.text();\n    if (!res.ok) {\n        throw new Error(`MCP HTTP ${res.status} ${res.statusText}: ${text.slice(0, 4000)}`);\n    }\n    let data;\n    try {\n        data = JSON.parse(text);\n    }\n    catch {\n        throw new Error(`MCP 返回非 JSON：${text.slice(0, 4000)}`);\n    }\n    if ('error' in data) {\n        throw new Error(`MCP error ${data.error.code}: ${data.error.message}`);\n    }\n    return unwrapJsonRpcResult(data.result);\n}\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// Scope 管理\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// 通用工具注册函数\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n/**\n * 注册 MCP 工具的通用函数 (使用 invoke 机制进行权限检查)\n */\nexport function registerMcpTool(api, config) {\n    const { toolClient, log } = createToolContext(api, config.name);\n    registerTool(api, {\n        name: config.name,\n        label: config.label,\n        description: config.description,\n        parameters: config.schema,\n        async execute(toolCallId, params) {\n            const p = params;\n            try {\n                log.debug?.(`Calling ${config.mcpToolName} (toolCallId: ${toolCallId})`);\n                const startTime = Date.now();\n                // 执行参数验证\n                config.validate?.(p);\n                const client = toolClient();\n                const brand = client.account.brand;\n                // 通过 invoke 进行权限检查并调用 MCP\n                // 严格模式：必须拥有 toolActionKey 所需的所有 scope\n                const result = await client.invoke(config.toolActionKey, async (_sdk, _opts, uat) => {\n                    // 权限检查已通过，直接使用 invoke 传入的 UAT\n                    if (!uat) {\n                        throw new Error('UAT not available');\n                    }\n                    return callMcpTool(config.mcpToolName, p, toolCallId, uat, brand);\n                }, {\n                    as: 'user',\n                });\n                const duration = Date.now() - startTime;\n                log.debug?.(`${config.mcpToolName} succeeded in ${duration}ms`);\n                // MCP tools/call 返回值已经是 { content: [{ type, text }] } 格式，\n                // 直接透传 content，避免被 formatToolResult 再包一层\n                // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any\n                if (isRecord(result) && Array.isArray(result.content)) {\n                    // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any\n                    const mcpContent = result.content;\n\n[28 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774003752748}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7372c37","parentId":"820dedd3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:49:28.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand. The MCP tools are called via HTTP POST to an MCP endpoint. The tool requires:\n1. An MCP endpoint URL\n2. A User Access Token (UAT) for authentication\n3. The tool call is made via JSON-RPC 2.0 protocol\n\nSince I'm running inside OpenClaw and the tools should be registered with the runtime, let me try to use the tool through the runtime's tool calling mechanism. However, I notice that I don't have direct access to call these tools via exec commands.\n\nLet me check if there's a simpler way. Perhaps I can write a Node.js script that calls the tool:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d655370a0cef487798bcfde9","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/tmp/update-doc.mjs","content":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n/**\n * Call feishu_update_doc MCP tool\n */\n\nimport { registerUpdateDocTool } from './update-wrapper.mjs';\n\n// Read params from command line or use defaults\nconst docId = process.argv[2] || 'WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd';\nconst mode = process.argv[3] || 'overwrite';\n\nconst markdown = `# 📝 飞书 Skill 功能讲解\n\n## 概述\n\n飞书文档管理助手提供完整的文档创建、读取、更新能力，基于 OpenClaw 的 MCP 工具集实现。\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 核心功能\n\n### 1️⃣ 文档创建 (feishu-create-doc)\n\n从 Lark-flavored Markdown 内容创建新的飞书云文档。\n\n**支持参数**:\n| 参数 | 必填 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| markdown | ✅ | 文档内容（Lark-flavored Markdown） |\n| title | ❌ | 文档标题 |\n| folder_token | ❌ | 父文件夹 token |\n| wiki_node | ❌ | 知识库节点 token |\n| wiki_space | ❌ | 知识空间 ID（my_library=个人知识库） |\n\n**返回值**:\n\\`\\`\\`json\n{\n  \"doc_id\": \"doxcnXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX\",\n  \"doc_url\": \"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/doxcnXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX\",\n  \"message\": \"文档创建成功\"\n}\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n<callout emoji=\"💡\" background-color=\"light-blue\">\n**最佳实践**：内容结构清晰，标题层级≤4 层，合理使用 Callout 高亮块突出关键信息\n</callout>\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ 文档读取 (feishu-fetch-doc)\n\n获取飞书云文档的 Markdown 内容。\n\n**功能特点**:\n- 返回标准 Markdown 格式\n- 支持处理文档中的图片、文件、画板\n- 配合 feishu_doc_media 工具下载资源\n\n---\n\n### 3️⃣ 文档更新 (feishu-update-doc)\n\n支持 7 种更新模式：\n\n| 模式 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| append | 追加到文档末尾 |\n| overwrite | 覆盖全文 |\n| prepend | 插入到文档开头 |\n| replace | 定位替换指定内容 |\n| insert_before | 在指定位置前插入 |\n| insert_after | 在指定位置后插入 |\n| delete | 删除指定内容 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 支持的块类型\n\n### 基础块类型\n\n| 类型 | 语法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 标题 | \\`#\\` ~ \\`######\\` | H1-H6，H7-H9 用\\`<h7>\\`~\\`<h9>\\` |\n| 段落 | 普通文本 | 支持对齐、颜色属性 |\n| 列表 | \\`-\\` / \\`1.\\` | 无序/有序列表，支持嵌套 |\n| 待办 | \\`- [ ]\\` / \\`- [x]\\` | 待办事项 |\n| 引用 | \\`>\\` | 引用块 |\n| 代码块 | \\` \\`\\`\\` \\` | 围栏代码块，支持多语言 |\n\n### 富文本格式\n\n| 格式 | 语法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 粗体 | \\`**文字**\\` | 加粗强调 |\n| 斜体 | \\`*文字*\\` | 斜体 |\n| 删除线 | \\`~~文字~~\\` | 删除线 |\n| 行内代码 | \\` \\`代码\\` \\` | 行内代码 |\n| 颜色 | \\`<text color=\"red\">\\` | 文字颜色/背景色 |\n| 链接 | \\`[文字](URL)\\` | 超链接 |\n\n### 高级块类型\n\n| 类型 | 语法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Callout | \\`<callout>\\` | 高亮块（提示/警告/成功） |\n| 分栏 | \\`<grid cols=\"2\">\\` | 2-5 列分栏布局 |\n| 表格 | \\`<lark-table>\\` | 增强表格，支持复杂内容 |\n| 图片 | \\`<image url=\"...\">\\` | 自动下载上传 |\n| 文件 | \\`<file url=\"...\">\\` | 文件卡片 |\n| Mermaid | \\` \\`\\`\\`mermaid \\` | 自动渲染为画板 |\n| 公式 | \\`$$\\` / \\`$\\` | LaTeX 数学公式 |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 使用示例\n\n### 创建简单文档\n\n# 项目计划\n\n## 目标\n\n- 目标 1\n- 目标 2\n\n### 创建带 Callout 的文档\n\n<callout emoji=\"💡\" background-color=\"light-blue\">\n重要需求说明\n</callout>\n\n## 功能列表\n\n| 功能 | 优先级 |\n|------|--------|\n| 登录 | P0 |\n| 导出 | P1 |\n\n### 创建带 Mermaid 图表的文档\n\n\\`\\`\\`mermaid\ngraph LR\n    A[开始] --> B[创建文档]\n    B --> C[编辑内容]\n    C --> D[发布]\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n---\n\n<callout emoji=\"✅\" background-color=\"light-green\">\n**文档有序，协作无忧** — 飞书文档管理助手\n</callout>\n`;\n\nconsole.log('Document ID:', docId);\nconsole.log('Mode:', mode);\nconsole.log('Markdown length:', markdown.length);\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":1461,"cacheRead":19125,"cacheWrite":1060,"totalTokens":21652,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00040908000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00040974}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774003752756}}
